Moje holka surfuje.

22
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:18,000
To mi stačí.

23
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,000
To je tak ubohý.

24
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,500
Takumi.

25
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,000
Co je?

26
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,000
Ale...

